# Email Configuration (optional - for ticket notifications)
# If not configured, emails will be skipped but registrations will still work

# Gmail example:
# SMTP_HOST=smtp.gmail.com
# SMTP_PORT=587
# SMTP_USER=your-email@gmail.com
# SMTP_PASS=your-app-password

# For Gmail, use App Password: https://myaccount.google.com/apppasswords
